{"tid":2418242,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Poly校長：理大事年「和平解決」、「能夠處理成這樣已經不錯」","createTime":"2021-02-22T12:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T16:57:31.000Z","uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"db8bc8050ad9ddc3309533e8200fba9ba4376b40","tid":2418242,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"麻煩咁多位post理大屠城嘅相出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界打仗都唔敢攻打人地嘅大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港警察做到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/appledailyhk/show/60339242d81d7014c4b6927c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fappledailyhk%2Fshow%2F60339242d81d7014c4b6927c&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=679e0960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/appledailyhk/show/60339242d81d7014c4b6927c</a><br />\n<br />\n「理大圍城」逾一年後，校長滕錦光接受報章專訪時首度提及事件，形容事件和平解決，稱最嚴重是有警察被箭射中，更自評「能夠處理成這樣已經不錯」。<br />\n<br />\n【理大圍城】 校長滕錦光稱「和平落幕」 警被箭射中「最嚴重」 自詡「處理不錯」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/SL3MGSC7T5FPXFRCZXCL3RIIXA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=mewe&amp;utm_content=post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FSL3MGSC7T5FPXFRCZXCL3RIIXA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dmewe%26utm_content%3Dpost&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=7eebe6e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210222%2FSL3MGSC7T5FPXFRCZXCL3RIIXA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dmewe%26utm_content%3Dpost&h=4b598222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210222/SL3MGSC7T5FPXFRCZXCL3RIIXA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nex